Duskfade is coming to PlayStation®5 in 2026. Wishlist Now!

Shatter the shackles of time as you jump, swing, and slash through a fantastic world in this love letter to classic 3D action platformers. Zirian, accompanied by his mechanical Cuckoo, must save his sister from a mysterious Clock Tower that has plunged the land into eternal night.

Duskfade is a heartfelt tribute to the golden age of 3D action-platformers, packed with tight, fluid gameplay, stunning world design, and a deeply emotional story that hits hard in all the right ways.

author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10007223

Go behind the scenes of Aphelion's original soundtrack with composer Amine Bouhafa.  

Amine Bouhafa takes us inside his studio to talk about composing music for DON'T NOD's upcoming sci-fi adventure game, Aphelion. Discover how he uses instruments such as the pipe organ and the rare Cristal Bachet to achieve his unique mix of epic and intimate.  

About the game  

As ESA astronauts Ariane and Thomas, explore and survey an uncharted planet and solve the mystery of your crash landing, all while trying to survive in the terrifying presence of an unknown enemy. At its heart, Aphelion is an emotional tale about love, resilience, hope, and what we bring with us when everything is lost.   

A game in collaboration with ESA, the European Space Agency.

Aphelion launches on PlayStation®5 in 2026. 

#ps5 #ps5games
title: Aphelion - A Musical Journey - Amine Bouhafa | PS5 Games
